      <title>日本股东大会拥挤引发投资者担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-10/japan-s-jammed-agm-season-raises-investors-concerns-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据日本交易所集团称，本月将有近 60% 的日本公司举行年度股东大会，其中 30% 将于 6 月 27 日举行。投资者担心这会限制股东参与度。佐野秀之在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-10/japan-s-jammed-agm-season-raises-investors-concerns-video</guid>
